title: Grateful Dead Live at Capital Centre on 1993-03-18
lineage: Tascam DA20 MKII->Edirol R44->SD->PC->CD Wave Editor->Flac Frontend; Tapers Unknown ,Eliot Byron's Rig,Eliot Byron's tape marked Master.
description:
Set 1

Hell In A Bucket-> Sugaree, Walkin' Blues, Broken Arrow, Loose Lucy, When I Paint My Masterpiece, Friend Of The Devil, The Music Never Stopped

Set 2

China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, Way To Go Home, Wave To The Wind-> Estimated Prophet-> Terrapin Station-> Jam-> Drums-> Jam-> Corinna-> Wharf Rat-> Throwing Stones-> Not Fade Away, E: I Fought The Law

Bruce Hornsby sat in for the whole 2nd set and encore on accordion
